{"word":"G1299 - διατάσσω - diatássō - dee-at-as'-so - Appoint","slug":"G1299","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">διατάσσω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>diatássō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>dee-at-as'-so"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Appoint"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"- Original: <b><el>διατάσσω</el></b> <p />- Transliteration: <b>Diatasso</b> <p />- Phonetic: <b>dee-at-as'-so</b> <p class=\"def\">- Definition: </p> <p class='li260'><b>1.</b> to arrange, appoint, ordain, prescribe, give order </p> <p class=\"origin\"/>- Origin: from <a href=\"#/G1223\">G1223</a> and <a href=\"#/G5021\">G5021</a> <p />- TDNT entry: 08:34,1 <p />- Part(s) of speech: Verb <p />- Strong's: From <a href=\"#/G1223\">G1223</a> and <a href=\"#/G5021\">G5021</a>; to <i>arrange thoroughly</i> that is (specifically) <i>institute prescribe</i> <b>etc.</b>: - appoint command give (set in) order ordain. "},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1296\">G1296</a>, <a href=\"#/G1297\">G1297</a>, <a href=\"#/G2004\">G2004</a>, <a href=\"#/G392\">G392</a>, <a href=\"#/G4367\">G4367</a>, <a href=\"#/G5001\">G5001</a>, <a href=\"#/G5021\">G5021</a>, <a href=\"#/G506\">G506</a>, <a href=\"#/G5292\">G5292</a>, <a href=\"#/G5293\">G5293</a>, <a href=\"#/G657\">G657</a>, <a href=\"#/G812\">G812</a>, <a href=\"#/G813\">G813</a>, <a href=\"#/G814\">G814</a>"}]}